data.description: The location for this home is the best of both worlds with over 10 acres, privacy, 5 acres of irrigation from TID, and yet only a few minutes to downtown Ashland, Shakespeare, restaurants and shopping. The home has 5 bedrooms, 3 including the primary suite on the main level, and 2 additional bedrooms on the lower level. One of the upstairs bathrooms was recently completely renovated. A 2000 square foot shop with concrete floor has two separate work rooms each with their own heating & AC systems and an office. One of the workrooms is ventilated. The irrigated terraced garden area would be a dream for a master gardener and has potential as a vineyard or family farm. The home also features wood framed windows, laminate & tile flooring, and Hunter Communications Business Class Internet.
